==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: do-it-yourselfer
<hw>do-it-yourselfer</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a person who often makes
objects typically made by professionals, or performs repairs typically
performed by professionals, though not having professional training in
the relevant art. The term is used mostly to refer to activities related
to maintaining a home.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Dokimastic</ent>⟦br⟧
